354
00:26:07,160 --> 00:26:07,839
[SPEAKER_02] šta mi se dogodilo,

355
00:26:07,839 --> 00:26:08,940
[SPEAKER_02] ja govorim, frazvijezdo,

356
00:26:08,940 --> 00:26:10,980
[SPEAKER_02] znači, to i to se dogodilo,

357
00:26:10,980 --> 00:26:11,940
[SPEAKER_02] znači, ja sam puka,

358
00:26:11,940 --> 00:26:12,900
