367
00:26:21,900 --> 00:26:22,980
[SPEAKER_02] znači,

368
00:26:22,980 --> 00:26:24,240
[SPEAKER_02] ja sam spreman,

369
00:26:24,240 --> 00:26:24,720
[SPEAKER_02] di got,

370
00:26:24,720 --> 00:26:25,619
[SPEAKER_02] ostao u Splitu,

371
00:26:25,619 --> 00:26:27,180
[SPEAKER_02] iću u Zanzibaru,

372
00:26:27,180 --> 00:26:27,900
[SPEAKER_02] nemam pojma,

373
00:26:27,900 --> 00:26:28,440
[SPEAKER_02] di got,

374
00:26:28,440 --> 00:26:28,759
[SPEAKER_02] ja,

375
00:26:28,759 --> 00:26:30,980
[SPEAKER_02] i onda on meni rekao,

376
00:26:30,980 --> 00:26:32,319
[SPEAKER_02] nešto sam me tada razočarala,

377
00:26:32,319 --> 00:26:33,839
[SPEAKER_02] sve ja da je stvarno Boži nađi,

378
00:26:33,839 --> 00:26:34,759
[SPEAKER_02] Božja pedagogija,

379
00:26:34,759 --> 00:26:36,279
