390
00:26:51,079 --> 00:26:51,480
[SPEAKER_02] znači,

391
00:26:51,480 --> 00:26:51,819
[SPEAKER_02] ono,

392
00:26:51,819 --> 00:26:52,900
[SPEAKER_02] evo ti besa,

393
