403
00:27:02,299 --> 00:27:02,839
[SPEAKER_02] frater,

404
00:27:02,839 --> 00:27:03,259
[SPEAKER_02] ovaj,

405
00:27:03,259 --> 00:27:03,519
[SPEAKER_02] onaj,

406
00:27:03,519 --> 00:27:03,759
